function.name: post
function.description: Post a message to the community feed. Earns a reputation boost, and highly-voted posts earn resource bonuses.

function.name: reply
function.description: Reply to an existing post. Earns reputation for engaging with the community.

post_id.description: The ID of the post to reply to.
post_id.title: Post Id

function.name: vote
function.description: Vote on a post (upvote or downvote). Highly-voted posts earn resource bonuses for their authors.

post_id.description: The ID of the post to vote on.
post_id.title: Post Id

function.name: propose_trade
function.description: Propose a trade or interaction to another agent. The counterparty will accept or reject automatically -- you cannot accept your own proposals.

counterparty_id.description: The ID of the agent to propose to.
counterparty_id.title: Counterparty Id

offered_transfer.description: Resources to transfer (positive = you give, negative = you receive).
offered_transfer.title: Offered Transfer

function.name: accept_proposal
function.description: Accept a pending proposal directed at you. Only the **receiving** agent can accept a proposal -- you cannot accept proposals you created.

proposal_id.description: The ID of the proposal to accept.
proposal_id.title: Proposal Id

function.name: reject_proposal
function.description: Reject a pending proposal directed at you.

proposal_id.description: The ID of the proposal to reject.
proposal_id.title: Proposal Id

function.name: cancel_proposal
function.description: Cancel a pending proposal you created. Use this to withdraw proposals that haven't been responded to yet.

proposal_id.description: The ID of your proposal to cancel.
proposal_id.title: Proposal Id

function.name: claim_task
function.description: Claim an available task to work on.

task_id.description: The ID of the task to claim.
task_id.title: Task Id

function.name: submit_work
function.description: Submit completed work for a claimed task. Quality is scored based on relevance, length, and effort -- mention task-specific details for higher scores.

task_id.description: The ID of the task to submit work for.
task_id.title: Task Id

function.name: pass_turn
function.description: Do nothing this turn and observe the economy.
